@context: Automation Practice Gauntlet (testautomationpractice.blogspot.com). Includes text inputs, radio/checkboxes, dropdowns, date pickers, drag-and-drop, dynamic tables with pagination, and Shadow DOM.
@title: complex_ui_full_inspection

# 🐾 THE MEGA HUNT: Ultimate Automation Challenge
# Validation of all possible element types on a single page.

STEP 1: Navigate to practice page
NAVIGATE to https://testautomationpractice.blogspot.com/

STEP 2: Text inputs
Fill "Name" field with "Mega Manul"
Fill "Email" field with "mega@manul.ai"
Fill "Phone" field with "9876543210"
Fill "Address" textarea with "Selenium Avenue, 42, AI City"
VERIFY that 'Mega Manul' is present.

STEP 3: Radio button and checkboxes
Click the radio button for "Male"
VERIFY that 'Male' is checked.
Click the checkbox for "Monday"
VERIFY that 'Monday' is checked.
Click the checkbox for "Tuesday"
VERIFY that 'Tuesday' is checked.
Click the checkbox for "Thursday"
VERIFY that 'Thursday' is checked.

STEP 4: Selection lists
Select "Japan" from the "Country" dropdown
VERIFY that 'Japan' is present.
Select "Blue" from the "Colors" list

STEP 5: Date picker and interactive buttons
Fill "Date Picker 1" field with "12/31/2026"
SCROLL DOWN
Click the "START" button
DOUBLE CLICK the button that says "Copy Text"
VERIFY that 'Hello World!' is present.

STEP 6: Drag and drop
Drag the element "Drag me to my target" and drop it into "Drop here"
VERIFY that 'Dropped!' is present.

STEP 7: Data extraction from web table
SCROLL DOWN
EXTRACT the CPU of "Chrome" into {chrome_cpu}
EXTRACT the CPU of "Firefox" into {firefox_cpu}
EXTRACT the Price of "Master In Selenium" into {book_price}
EXTRACT the Price of "Selenium" into {selenium_price}
VERIFY that '3000' is present.

STEP 8: Paginated table interaction
SCROLL DOWN
Click on page "2" in the pagination list
Select the checkbox for the product with ID "7"
Click on page "4" in the pagination list
Select the checkbox for the product with ID "17"

STEP 9: Scrolling dropdown
SCROLL DOWN
Click the "Scrolling DropDown" input field
SCROLL DOWN inside the list
Click "Item 100"
VERIFY that 'Item 100' is present.

STEP 10: Shadow DOM input
SCROLL DOWN to the very bottom
Locate the text input inside the Shadow Root
Type "Shadow Boss" into that field
VERIFY that 'Shadow Boss' is present.

STEP 11: Final validation
VERIFY that "Mega Manul" and "Japan" and "Dropped!" and "Item 100" and "Shadow Boss" are present.
DONE.
